This paper is about the identification of semantic relations using a combination of path-based and distributional methods, which are commonly used in natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI), machine learning algorithms (cs.LG), information retrieval methods (cs.IR), and computational complexity analysis (cs.CC).
